WEBVTT

00:00:07.818 --> 00:00:14.080
2008-yil arxeologlar 9000 yoshdagi 2 ta 
skelet qoldiqlarini topdilar.

00:00:14.080 --> 00:00:17.731
Qadimgi odamlar o'limi sabablarini 
aniqlashning iloji yo'q, ammo

00:00:17.731 --> 00:00:24.131
ularning suyaklari bizga ma'lum bakteriya 
bilan kasallanganligi ayon bo'ldi.

00:00:24.131 --> 00:00:28.352
Qadimgi yunonlar 
bu kasallikni phthisis (sil),

00:00:28.352 --> 00:00:34.451
inklar chaki-onki, inglizlar esa 
tuberkulyoz deb yuritishgan.